  "text": "Okay, this is the central important point. Why then was it so you've answered this, but it seemed to me that if the polarization was the obvious thing, that more effort would have been put forward to polarize. Let me see if I can state this. Before the veil, there was an awareness of the need for polarization toward service to others in third density by all entities, whether incarnate, in third density yellow ray bodies, or whether in between incarnations. I am wow. You begin to grasp the situation. Let us continue the metaphor of the schooling, but consider the scholar as a being an entity in your younger years of the schooling process. The entity is fed, clothed, and protected, regardless of whether or not the school work is accomplished. Therefore, the entity does not do the homework, but rather enjoys playtime, mealtime and vacation. It is not until there is a reason to wish to excel that most entities will attempt to excel.",
